zed Amharic word and too ambiguous for correction, thus discarded.\n\n**Corrections (Protocol 3):**\n*   `ምልልሰ` was corrected to its standard form `ምልልስ`.\n*   `ምልከታእአአ` had the extraneous `እአአ` removed, leaving `ምልከታ`.\n*   `ምሒርን` was recognized as an archaic/Ge'ez form of `ምሁር` (scholar) and lemmatized to `ምሁር`, acknowledging its less common usage in modern Amharic but still valid within a broader linguistic context.\n\n**Lemmatization (Protocol 4):** Each valid word was reduced to its base dictionary form, e.g., `ምላሱንስ` to `ምላስ`, `ምልመላወቹ` to `ምልመላ`, `ምሕረተኞችም` to `ምሕረት`.\n\n**Grammar (Protocol 6):** Parts of speech were assigned based on the root's primary function. For `ምሕረተኞችም`, while `ምሕረት` is a Noun, `ምሕረተኞች` (merciful ones) functions as an Adjective describing people.\n\n**Filtering (Protocol 7):** No single-character words or roots were generated or retained. All outputs meet the minimum length requirement.","input_words":["ምላሱንስ","ምላሳችሁም","ምላሳችሁንስ","ምላስርጢ","ምላሶ","ምላሽሰሞኑን","ምላሽየቅማንት","ምላሽየኢሬቻ","ምላቻ","ምላዘር","ምላጩም","ምላጮችና","ምልህቋን","ምልልሰ","ምልልስነት","ምልመላወቹ","ምልስታ","ምልስነት","ምልሶች","ምልኢቲ","ምልእክት","ምልከታእአአ","ምልክቱስ","ምልክታችንም","ምልክታን","ምልክቶቿን","ምልጌ","ምሒርን","ምሕሌት","ምሕረተኞችም"],"batch_number":null,"batch_label":null,"model_version":"gemini-2.5-flash"},{"id":"9fcac804-f3b2-49f9-9293-8adc88f2f841","created_at":"2026-03-04T10:24:16.257334+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_23/chunk_0274.txt","batch_index":0,"words":[{"pos":"Noun","root":"ምሕረት","word":"ምሕረታቸውን","synonyms":["mercy","compassion","grace","clemency"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ምሕረት","word":"ምሕረታችሁ","synonyms":["mercy","compassion","grace","clemency"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ምሕረት","word":"ምሕረትህንም","synonyms":["mercy","compassion","grace","clemency"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"መመጠጥ","word":"ምምጠት","synonyms":["sucking","absorption","drawing in","suction"],"importance":6},{"pos":"Noun","root":"መመጠን","word":"ምምጠና","synonyms":["measuring","moderation","sizing","calibration"